items.name: Taskmanager
items.description: This is a Python-based Task Manager application that provides real-time monitoring of system performance. Built with Tkinter, psutil, and GPUtil, it displays live data on CPU usage, memory consumption, disk activity, and GPU status in a simple graphical interface. Ideal for keeping track of system resources and managing performance.
